Tremor looked to Slugslinger.  "You to Slugface.  By the way, 
Quake was to old a name for me, it's Tremor now."
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

JetV looked back to Artemis.  "Umm....I guess we fight" he said, 
though all he wanted to do was get into the woods, away from the 
danger.

"Pacifix, this is JetV.  We have what do you call, a situation out 
here." 

With that he fired four shots from his shotgun attached to his side 
in this mode.
